			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_25962783">		 &lt;<a href="mailto:slashdot1729%40g%5B+%5Dl.com+%5B'mai'+in+gap%5D">slashdot1729@g[ ]l.com ['mai' in gap]</a>&gt;
