			<h4><a id="comment_link_25959965" name="comment_link_25959965" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1048087&amp;cid=25959965" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(25959965)">Re:Mine was certainly cruel to us</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_25959965" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 25959965); return false">Score:5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~chrb">chrb <span class="uid">(1083577)</span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_25959965">		
		on Tuesday December 02 2008, @10:33AM (<a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1048087&amp;cid=25959965">#25959965</a>)
		<small> </small>
